OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will often be large
OL,6,Famounts of cloud, but still bright and
OL,7,Fperhaps sunny spells will occur with
OL,8,Fall areas remaining dry. Feeling warm
OL,9,For very warm in the light winds away
OL,10,Ffrom the coast, where light onshore
OL,11,Fbreezes develop.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry and becoming largely
OL,14,Fcloud free, allowing a sunny end to
OL,15,Fthe day for most places and then a
OL,16,Fclear night, However, patchy mist may
OL,17,Fdevelop later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
