OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSunny start for most places,
OL,6,Fwith any early mist quickly clearing.
OL,7,FCloud then spreads across the region,
OL,8,Fbut it will remain dry, bright and
OL,9,Fwarm or very warm. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBreezy
OL,12,Fat times with variable cloud for much
OL,13,Fof the period, staying mostly dry.
OL,14,FTemperatures likely above average,
OL,15,Fperhaps becoming very warm or hot in
OL,16,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
